# BookShelf API - Authentication Endpoints

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5093/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5093/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:5093/api/Auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "your-jwt-token",
  "refreshToken": "your-refresh-token"
}

### Get User Profile
GET http://localhost:5093/api/Auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token

### Request Password Reset
POST http://localhost:5093/api/Auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

### Reset Password
POST http://localhost:5093/api/Auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "reset-token",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!"
}